snippet.title: The Sims 4 Get to Work: Official Scientist Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Conduct experiments and create awesome inventions as a Scientist in The Sims 4 Get to Work Expansion Pack.

Learn more: http://bit.ly/1wvAgzk

Actively control your Sims at their workplace in The Sims 4 Get to Work, available April 2015.
